OL,5, Beauty giant Avon has come under fire  
OL,6, for maintaining links with Russia      
OL,7, despite the ongoing war in Ukraine.    
OL,9,FThe BBC has discovered the firm is     
OL,10,Fstill recruiting new sales agents in   
OL,11,Fthe country and continuing production  
OL,12,Fin a huge plant in the Moscow region.  
OL,14,FAvon, which has its headquarters in the
OL,15,FUK, started doing business in Russia 30
OL,16,Fyears ago.                             
OL,18,FThe firm said that it provides         
OL,19,F"critical support" for women whose     
OL,20,Flivelihoods depend on their business.  
